lead_paragraph: Inter Milan clinched fourth place in Serie A after a 2-1 home victory over Empoli on Saturday while AC Milan gave their European aspirations a boost with a 1-0 triumph over 10-man Bologna.

headline.print_headline: Inter Secure Fourth Spot, Milan Boost European Hopes
